Question 2. Modify your code in part 1 to turn the motor clockwise when you press 1 and anticlockwise when you press 2. [50] 
The desired functionalities for validating QUESTION 2 are listed in TABLE II with four states. Notably, 
these states should be able to switch smoothly during the evaluation procedure. Meanwhile, the updated 
frequency in the EdSim51 simulator is recommended to set at 1Hz or 100Hz for evaluating the 
effectiveness.
TABLE II
REQUIRED FUNCTIONALITY OF QUESTION 2
State Key 1 Key 2 Motor
0 Released Released Stop
1 Pressed Released Clockwise
2 Released Pressed Anti-clockwise
3 Pressed Pressed Stop
